div.div:
I, the protagonist, was just an ordinary high school girl, but suddenly I was reincarnated as a spider monster in a fantasy world. Not only that, but I awakened in a dungeon filled with vicious monsters. Armed with only my human knowledge and my overwhelming positivity, I'm forced to use spiderwebs and traps to defeat far stronger monsters just to stay alive... So begins the labyrinth survival story of a girl with incredible mental strength living as one of the lowest-ranked beasts!
(Source: Crunchyroll)

Kirishima Tooru was accustomed to solving all problems through violence and was called the Demon of Sakuragi. One day, the boss of the Sakuragi family suddenly summons Kirishima and appoints him caretaker of his only daughter, Yaeka! A heartwarming comedy about a yakuza crime familys right-hand man and the boss only daughter. The two of them are about to begin their new daily lives together!
(Source: Crunchyroll, edited)
Tensei Reijou wa Boukensha wo Kokorozasu

The fluffy and strongest Holy Beast! One day Seraphione, a nobleman's daughter, met Roux and recalled her previous life's memories of a japanese woman in her thirties. [I've been reborn in another world, and not only that but I'm a villainess--!?] If they find out about my cheat magic then it means the destruction end!
However, although she knows that, she still loves magic and carelessly enters into a magical contract with Roux. If it continues like this it'll become dangerous! In that case let's train and aim to become an adventurer!
(Source: Kadokawa, translated)
Danshi Koukousei wo Yashinaitai Onee-san no Hanashi
Comedy, Ecchi, Romance, Slice of Life

When Minoru's parents ran out on him and their debt collectors started shaking him down, it was the kind lady next door who took him in. She offers to have him live with her, but she seems awfully excited about the idea...and suddenly Minoru's wondering just what he got himself into! (Source: BOOK WALKER)

div.span: Turbulent Adventurers are Introverted, Observant, Feeling, Prospecting and Turbulent. They tend to have open minds, approaching life, new experiences, and people with grounded warmth.
Likely prefers fewer, yet deep and meaningful, social interactions and feels drawn to calmer environments.
Likely pragmatic and down-to-earth, with a strong focus on what is happening or very likely to happen.
Likely values emotional expression and sensitivity, prioritizing empathy, social harmony, and cooperation.
Likely very good at improvising and adapting. Tends to be flexible and values novelty above stability.
Likely self-conscious, sensitive to stress, success-driven, perfectionistic, and eager to improve.
